# ── Go build artifacts ────────────────────────────
# `make all` cross-compiles here; never commit the matrix output.
dist/
# local build/verify scratch binaries
sshvault-verify
sshvault-built
*.test
*.out
coverage*

# ── alternative prebuilt binaries ─────────────────
# We commit only the canonical `sshvault` (linux) + `sshvault.exe` (windows).
# Other arches are produced on demand via `make all` / CI releases.
sshvault-linux-amd64
sshvault-linux-arm64
sshvault-darwin-amd64
sshvault-darwin-arm64
sshvault-windows-amd64.exe

# ── secrets / runtime (never commit) ──────────────
# Private keys and ssh-agent env must never land in the vault repo.
id_ed25519
id_rsa
id_ecdsa
*.pem
agent.env

# ── editor ────────────────────────────────────────
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*~
